snippet.textDisplay:
Waise maza araha hai full time is dafa Coke mein!! Rohail bhai ki jeet hai. He's back with vengeance! 
Beautiful composition of majors, minors, relatives and dissonance!!! Beautiful composition!!! After Zoe, this is the other personal favorite!!!! 
 Zeb never fails to impress!!! Bass is also doing crazy stuff, really good that Rohail is letting people open up and feel free. This is the result!  Pure magic!!! 
I thought in the end, the song would really pick up and go crazy, but it's perfect this way, unexpected!
